# Assets Folder for Bike Mechanic Frontend

This directory is intended to hold your frontend static assets for the bike mechanic website, such as:

- Images (jpg, png, webp)
- Icons (if using custom SVG icons)
- Fonts (only if using locally hosted fonts, otherwise use Google Fonts CDN)
- Other static files (videos, PDFs, etc.)

---

### Folder structure recommendation:

assets/
├── images/
│   ├── hero-bike.jpg
│   ├── gallery/
│   │   ├── bike-maintenance1.jpg
│   │   ├── mechanic-fixing-tire.jpg
│   │   ├── bike-tools.jpg
│   │   ├── bike-brake-repair.jpg
│   │   ├── bike-gear-closeup.jpg
│   │   └── bike-workshop.jpg
│   └── about-shop.jpg
└── icons/
    └── (optional SVG icons if used)

---

### How to use local images in your HTML:

Replace the external URLs (e.g., Unsplash.com URLs) with the relative paths to images in your assets folder.

Example:

Instead of:

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518655048521-f130df041f66?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;w=1470&amp;q=80" alt="Bike mechanic at work" />

Use:

<img src="assets/images/hero-bike.jpg" alt="Bike mechanic at work" />

Similarly for gallery images, for example:

<img src="assets/images/gallery/bike-maintenance1.jpg" alt="Bike maintenance work" />

---


